org.cell2d.space

Class CircleHitbox

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.cell2d.space.Hitbox
      • org.cell2d.space.CircleHitbox

  • public class CircleHitbox
extends Hitbox

    A CircleHitbox is a circular Hitbox with its origin at its center. A CircleHitbox's radius cannot be negative.
